show.description: When poor and desperate Radhika struggles to pay for her mother’s treatment, the cunning and wealthy Janvi offers her a shocking deal  to impersonate her and deceive Sameer. What begins as a lie spirals into a web of love, revenge, and secrets where the line between real and fake blurs dangerously. Watch Now!
